metadata.name: Cyber city
metadata.description:
An AI generated artwork of the theme cyber city. This artwork was created as part of an AI contest conducted by Magicalords. 
A total of 26 artworks were selected from 1000 + artworks. This image was selected and is exhibited at Spatialrx gallery.

The Curation of the artworks was done by 
Mark Kelly (Twitter: @saucebook ) and  
Pardis Firoozmand (Twitter: @pardis_world)

Image details

Dimension - 4266 x 4266 pixels  
Resolution - 300 dpi  
File Format - PNG  
Size - 21.5 MB
